  <project_license>GPL-3.0-or-later</project_license>

  <description>

    <p><em>GeoGebra Discovery</em> is an experimental version of GeoGebra. It contains some bleeding edge features of
    GeoGebra that are under heavy development and therefore not intended for every day use yet,
    so they are not included in the official GeoGebra version.</p>
    </description>

    <launchable type="desktop-id">io.github.kovzol.geogebra-discovery.desktop</launchable>

