  <releases>
    <release version="5.0.641.0" date="2026-01-31">
    <url type="details">https://github.com/kovzol/geogebra/commits/241a6e7d02adb6d2c126ef5c07d22a8536aa1bd5</url>
      <description>
        <p>Release description</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Improve CAS Export to Maple (Factor, Derivative, Integral, Limit)</li>
            <li>Implement checking equality with a certain angle (CNI)</li>
          </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
    <release version="5.0.641.0" date="2026-01-06">
    <url type="details">https://github.com/kovzol/geogebra/commits/225e9d22cc74f9c0dc22e3585ff61199cd596fb4</url>
      <description>
        <p>Release description</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Lazy initialization of Tarski to save time on startup</li>
            <li>First prototype to implement certain GeoGebra commands to Maple</li>
            <li>Re-add info on other webservices on command line</li>
            <li>Improve presentation of AreConcurrent (CNI)</li>
          </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
    <release version="5.0.641.0" date="2025-11-01">
    <url type="details">https://github.com/kovzol/geogebra/commits/b517deab97b922dfec59bd91a3fd76f4af78f337</url>
      <description>
        <p>Release description</p>
          <ul>
            <li>The CNI method has been updated by implementing several construction steps.</li>
            <li>The <em>ShowProof</em> command now supports Recio's method as well.</li>
            <li>Implement simple degree computation for the (Recio–)Chroman–Goel–Mudgal–Zveryk–Molnar-Szabo method</li>
          </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
  </releases>

